I wanted to show him you
weren't in danger,

00:12:27.933 --> 00:12:29.466
but that led me to
putting him in danger!

00:12:30.933 --> 00:12:33.066
Look out!

00:12:33.066 --> 00:12:34.300
Yuya!

00:12:34.300 --> 00:12:36.066
Get outta here!

00:12:36.066 --> 00:12:37.933
Take care
of Zuzu for me!

00:12:40.800 --> 00:12:42.433
That means...

00:12:42.433 --> 00:12:44.433
It's all my fault
Yuya's in trouble.

00:12:48.633 --> 00:12:51.600
Zuzu...

00:12:51.600 --> 00:12:54.233
(man)
You want a cerebral
restrictor for Yuya?

00:12:54.233 --> 00:12:55.966
(Jean Michel Rochet)
Yes.

00:12:55.966 --> 00:12:59.100
The restrictor will allow me
to directly control him,

00:12:59.100 --> 00:13:01.600
the same way
I control Sergey.

00:13:01.600 --> 00:13:03.100
<i>Are you sure, Director?</i>

00:13:03.100 --> 00:13:05.033
I mean, the one you
implanted in Sergey,

00:13:05.033 --> 00:13:07.400
the cerebral links
completely shorted out

00:13:07.400 --> 00:13:09.100
and nearly cooked
his cranium.

00:13:09.100 --> 00:13:10.766
We're barely
able to repair it.

00:13:10.766 --> 00:13:12.700
Don't you think it's
too dangerous?

00:13:12.700 --> 00:13:15.233
When will
it be ready?

00:13:15.233 --> 00:13:18.066
It'll take until
Midnight tonight.

00:13:18.066 --> 00:13:20.733
Then why are you wasting
time talking to me?

00:13:20.733 --> 00:13:22.066
You have one hour!

00:13:22.066 --> 00:13:24.866
The restrictor must be
in place and functional

00:13:24.866 --> 00:13:28.166
for Yuya's match
tomorrow.

00:13:28.166 --> 00:13:28.966
<i>Yes...</i>

00:13:28.966 --> 00:13:31.533
I understood,
Director.

00:13:31.533 --> 00:13:33.700
(Jean Michel Roget)
I have no doubt
that Duel Academy

00:13:33.700 --> 00:13:35.533
will invade New Domino City

00:13:35.533 --> 00:13:39.133
and steal away everything
that I have built!

00:13:39.133 --> 00:13:43.100
But I cannot and
will not let that happen!

00:13:43.100 --> 00:13:47.866
To fight against them, I will
need both Sergey and Yuya

00:13:47.866 --> 00:13:49.900
to battle
under my control.

00:13:54.066 --> 00:13:55.566
I can't keep
running forever.

00:13:55.566 --> 00:13:57.800
I don't care
about Security.

00:13:57.800 --> 00:14:00.000
I have to go
help Yuya.

00:14:00.000 --> 00:14:02.366
No way,
no how, Zuzu!

00:14:02.366 --> 00:14:05.366
Security's everywhere
what if they grab ya?

00:14:05.366 --> 00:14:08.400
Yeah, and lock ya up
in The Facility forever?

00:14:08.400 --> 00:14:09.700
I know...

00:14:09.700 --> 00:14:12.166
But that's a risk
I'm willing to take.

00:14:12.166 --> 00:14:15.500
You know why Security's
looking for you?

00:14:15.500 --> 00:14:16.900
Sure I do.

00:14:16.900 --> 00:14:19.300
I lost my duel so they
want to send me underground.

00:14:19.300 --> 00:14:21.466
You think they sent this
whole Security force out

00:14:21.466 --> 00:14:24.166
just to find some
girl who lost a match?

00:14:24.166 --> 00:14:26.666
Then why am
I so special?

00:14:26.666 --> 00:14:30.033
They have to find you
before Duel Academy does.

00:14:30.033 --> 00:14:33.166
Duel Academy's going to invade
this world sooner than later

00:14:33.166 --> 00:14:35.000
and try to
take you away.

00:14:35.000 --> 00:14:37.366
And I can't let
that happen.

00:14:37.366 --> 00:14:39.366
So you running around
trying to save Yuya

00:14:39.366 --> 00:14:41.433
isn't an
option right now.

00:14:41.433 --> 00:14:44.233
I'm not letting you out
of my sight again Zuzu.

00:14:44.233 --> 00:14:46.800
You're staying put.

00:14:46.800 --> 00:14:50.766
Sora... so you're
totally on our side now.

00:14:50.766 --> 00:14:53.066
And you're gonna fight
against Duel Academy?

00:14:53.066 --> 00:14:54.266
Well...

00:14:54.266 --> 00:14:56.333
Well what, Sora?

00:14:56.333 --> 00:14:59.400
Are you or
aren't you?

00:14:59.400 --> 00:15:00.766
Look, Zuzu.

00:15:00.766 --> 00:15:03.900
Duel Academy's been my
home for my entire life.

00:15:03.900 --> 00:15:05.600
But you know what
they've done!

00:15:05.600 --> 00:15:08.533
You can't let the past
control what you do now.

00:15:08.533 --> 00:15:10.700
You have to fight for
what you think is right.

00:15:13.466 --> 00:15:15.500
You make it
sound so easy.

00:15:15.500 --> 00:15:18.900
But I was brought up and
raised by Duel Academy.

00:15:18.900 --> 00:15:20.700
I was one of their
elite fighters.

00:15:20.700 --> 00:15:23.433
They taught me
everything I know.

00:15:23.433 --> 00:15:25.066
What's he
talking about?

00:15:25.066 --> 00:15:28.033
What's this Duel Academy
mumbo jumbo?

00:15:28.033 --> 00:15:29.966
I heard Zuzu say
somethin' about it

00:15:29.966 --> 00:15:33.133
and it sure
sounded scary.

00:15:33.133 --> 00:15:35.133
Yeah...
I remember.

00:15:35.133 --> 00:15:36.633
But these two
are friends.

00:15:36.633 --> 00:15:39.900
Why would Sora's people wanna
come here and attack us?

00:15:39.900 --> 00:15:41.533
We are friends.

00:15:41.533 --> 00:15:44.200
So that's why I'm
helping you out Zuzu.

00:15:44.200 --> 00:15:47.000
Even though the invasion
can't be stopped...

00:15:47.000 --> 00:15:49.566
I can still
help you out.

00:15:49.566 --> 00:15:51.933
I should have done this
when I first found you.

00:15:51.933 --> 00:15:55.666
It was foolish of me to
wait and risk your safety.

00:15:55.666 --> 00:15:58.133
What're you doing?

00:15:58.133 --> 00:16:00.400
I'm sending
you home, Zuzu.

00:16:00.400 --> 00:16:03.066
Back to your family
and friends.

00:16:03.066 --> 00:16:04.400
Sora!

00:16:04.400 --> 00:16:05.833
No, you won't!

00:16:05.833 --> 00:16:08.533
I'm not abandoning
my friends.

00:16:08.533 --> 00:16:12.066
Either we all go home
together, or none of us go!

00:16:12.066 --> 00:16:13.900
That's the only way.

00:16:13.900 --> 00:16:15.733
I will not leave
my friends behind.

00:16:17.833 --> 00:16:21.900
Come on Zuzu, I know
how you feel but...

00:16:21.900 --> 00:16:23.000
Who's there?

00:16:27.666 --> 00:16:30.533
Who's there?

00:16:30.533 --> 00:16:32.666
It is I,
Moon Shadow.

00:16:32.666 --> 00:16:37.166
You may not know me, but
you know my brother Sun Shadow.

00:16:37.166 --> 00:16:39.300
You turned him into a card

00:16:39.300 --> 00:16:43.266
and now you will
pay for your actions.

00:16:43.266 --> 00:16:46.200
I know in my heart his
spirit led me here to you,

00:16:46.200 --> 00:16:50.200
finally face‐to‐face, so I
can battle to avenge him!

00:16:50.200 --> 00:16:51.833
No, Moon Shadow!

00:16:51.833 --> 00:16:54.866
We're all on the same
team now, he's one of us!

00:16:54.866 --> 00:16:56.733
He is no ally
of mine!

00:16:56.733 --> 00:16:58.833
He is my
sworn enemy!

00:16:58.833 --> 00:17:00.166
Not anymore!

00:17:00.166 --> 00:17:01.666
Tell him, Sora...

00:17:01.666 --> 00:17:04.200
Tell him you don't do
stuff like that anymore!

00:17:04.200 --> 00:17:06.466
Moon Shadow,
Sora's our friend.

00:17:06.466 --> 00:17:09.733
He saved me and he's trying
to get us all home.

00:17:09.733 --> 00:17:11.800
And I'm going to...

00:17:11.800 --> 00:17:15.100
I will get you back to
your friends and family.

00:17:15.100 --> 00:17:17.400
And like you said,
I'm going to make sure

00:17:17.400 --> 00:17:19.433
no one gets
left behind!

00:17:23.600 --> 00:17:26.466
I apologize for what I
did to your brother,

00:17:26.466 --> 00:17:30.033
and I know just being sorry
about it doesn't bring him back.

00:17:30.033 --> 00:17:34.200
If my apology isn't enough, you
can do whatever you want to me.

00:17:34.200 --> 00:17:36.733
The only thing I ask is that
you give me enough time

00:17:36.733 --> 00:17:38.566
to keep my
promise to Yuya.

00:17:38.566 --> 00:17:40.266
Promise?

00:17:40.266 --> 00:17:42.966
I promised Yuya that
I'd protect Zuzu,

00:17:42.966 --> 00:17:46.733
and that's one
promise that I want to keep.

00:17:46.733 --> 00:17:48.733
You gotta at least
give me that.

00:17:51.733 --> 00:17:54.600
Zuzu, you know yourself that
you can't be running around

00:17:54.600 --> 00:17:56.700
with Security
on every corner.

00:17:56.700 --> 00:18:01.333
Since you can't get to Yuya,
I'll bring Yuya to you,

00:18:01.333 --> 00:18:03.733
it's the only option.

00:18:03.733 --> 00:18:06.666
And then Moon Shadow,
I'm all yours.

00:18:06.666 --> 00:18:08.433
Do whatever
you like.

00:18:08.433 --> 00:18:10.100
I'm at
your mercy.

00:18:13.733 --> 00:18:15.733
Agreed.

00:18:15.733 --> 00:18:18.500
Until then, I will keep Zuzu
and the children safe.

00:18:18.500 --> 00:18:20.666
I know of a secret
place in the underground

00:18:20.666 --> 00:18:23.933
hidden from prying eyes
of Sector Securty.

00:18:23.933 --> 00:18:25.566
The underground's
bad news!

00:18:25.566 --> 00:18:27.500
Are they gonna make us
work hard all the time

00:18:27.500 --> 00:18:29.133
if we go down
there with you?

00:18:29.133 --> 00:18:30.766
Why can't we
stay here?

00:18:30.766 --> 00:18:33.900
It may be hard for you to
believe because you are children

00:18:33.900 --> 00:18:35.600
with teeny‐weeny thoughts,

00:18:35.600 --> 00:18:37.100
but the Underground
is much safer

00:18:37.100 --> 00:18:38.766
than the streets
of this city

00:18:38.766 --> 00:18:42.733
with hundreds of Sector
Security forces around.

00:18:42.733 --> 00:18:45.866
They've even taken control
of the High Council.

00:18:45.866 --> 00:18:48.133
When there is nowhere
safe above ground,

00:18:48.133 --> 00:18:51.466
even the mighty
grizzly hides below.

00:18:51.466 --> 00:18:52.900
Worry not.

00:18:52.900 --> 00:18:55.033
I promise you
will be safe there.

00:18:55.033 --> 00:18:57.633
We will have the help of
the Lancers underground

00:18:57.633 --> 00:18:59.600
to assure it.

00:18:59.600 --> 00:19:01.133
Alright.

00:19:01.133 --> 00:19:04.133
At least I know we
have friends down there.

00:19:04.133 --> 00:19:06.266
