And up here.

00:19:06.266 --> 00:19:08.933
I told you I'd bring Yuya
to you and I will.

00:19:08.933 --> 00:19:11.166
And I'll make sure both
of you and all your friends

00:19:11.166 --> 00:19:12.633
can go home together.

00:19:12.633 --> 00:19:13.633
Right.

00:19:13.633 --> 00:19:14.633
I trust you.

00:19:14.633 --> 00:19:16.300
Because you're a
great friend, Sora.

00:19:16.300 --> 00:19:19.800
And what's more,
you're my teacher.

00:19:19.800 --> 00:19:23.400
If you can't trust your
teacher, who can you trust?

00:19:23.400 --> 00:19:26.366
Zuzu...

00:19:26.366 --> 00:19:28.500
Your form's
totally terrible!

00:19:28.500 --> 00:19:30.800
It's elbows in
like this!

00:19:30.800 --> 00:19:34.433
It still show's that there is a
lot you have to learn from me,

00:19:34.433 --> 00:19:35.633
a lot!

00:19:35.633 --> 00:19:37.133
(giggling)

00:19:43.333 --> 00:19:46.533
Well, I sure do hope y'all
are ready for the next dustup!

